snippet.title: Garbage Trailer
snippet.description:
Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1253710/Garbage/

Garbage is a fighting simulator game for PC. Experience the struggle which a homeless man goes through in a humorous manner. Primitive elements of contemporary life that we take for granted, such as staying warm, well-nourished, and hygienic, will become an issue.
